            "title": "今日我咁睇｜減息預期大降 阿里騰訊齊炒 港股料整固｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.yBUjPxsi6dvo3gjIo4YBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/9786680fb9880cb9300f7f55f4e6fd2c\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.美國聯儲局放鷹，市場對今年的降息預期迅速降溫，特別是鮑威爾「曾內部討論加息」，震散一眾股票商品投資者，實際上，近期除了原油外，其他商品價格都明顯下跌，金銀亦沒有避險作用，反而加密貨幣跌定先，現在沒那麼傷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.小編原本以為阿里對AI的著墨會更多，結果再令市場失望，今日股價料差不多跌至前底，但估計下跌空間有限，輕倉的可以入一注博彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. AI大模型的股份今日有所反彈，正如之前所言，阿里騰訊一齊燒錢搞AI，芯片、大模型這類公司自然受惠，Minimax、智譜、華虹半導體及中芯等都是觀察的對象，值博率比阿里更高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1b4e2001-f4b7-39e3-b82e-543469811646-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4. 港股今日曾回試25500點，先等企穩再考慮入貨，阻力位則在25800點及26000點，不過今日在阿里拖累下升至阻力位機會不大，先在25200點至25500點之間炒區間。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證街貨比例回升至64%，短期內基本因素或相反理論都不支持大市向上，炒上落為上策。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%8D-%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E9%BD%8A%E7%82%92-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E6%96%99%E6%95%B4%E5%9B%BA-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000846.html",
